sql: SELECT * FROM common.login_user LIMIT 5
SELECT table_schema, table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_schema NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') AND (table_name ILIKE '%user%' OR table_name ILIKE '%client%')
SELECT table_schema, table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_schema NOT IN ('pg_catalog', 'information_schema') ORDER BY table_schema, table_name
SELECT table_schema, table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_name ILIKE '%robot%' OR table_name ILIKE '%device%' OR table_name ILIKE '%agent%'
SELECT table_schema, table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_name ILIKE '%bot%'
SELECT request_id, consult_status, status_date, consult_ward_desc FROM patients.consultations WHERE case_id = 11857935 ORDER BY request_id
SELECT case_id, COUNT(*) as cnt FROM patients.consultations GROUP BY case_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT case_id, COUNT(*) as cnt FROM patients.consultations GROUP BY case_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 3 ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT request_id, case_id, consult_status, status_date FROM patients.consultations ORDER BY case_id, status_date LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT consult_status, COUNT(*) as cnt FROM patients.consultations GROUP BY consult_status ORDER BY cnt DESC LIMIT 20
SELECT DISTINCT consult_status, COUNT(*) as cnt FROM patients.consultations GROUP BY consult_status ORDER BY cnt DESC
SELECT DISTINCT consult_status FROM patients.consultations WHERE consult_status IS NOT NULL ORDER BY consult_status
UPDATE common.screen_settings SET agg_info_by = '97,38,29,31' WHERE screen_id = 'delayedImaging' RETURNING *
SELECT column_id, column_name, column_key, heb_name FROM common.column_settings WHERE LOWER(column_name) LIKE '%status%' OR LOWER(heb_name) LIKE '%סטטוס%' ORDER BY column_id
SELECT * FROM common.screen_settings WHERE screen_id = 'delayedImaging'
SELECT column_name FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_schema = 'patients' AND table_name = 'transport' ORDER BY ordinal_position
SELECT column_name FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_name = 'transport' AND table_schema = 'patients' AND column_name LIKE '%status%' OR column_name LIKE '%desc%'
SELECT table_name FROM information_schema.tables WHERE table_name LIKE '%transport%'
SELECT screen_id, screen_label, feature_order FROM common.screen_settings WHERE screen_id = 'delayedImaging'
SELECT * FROM common.column_settings WHERE column_name LIKE '%transport%' OR heb_name LIKE '%שינוע%'
